<HEAD>Suit Made For `The King' Stolen From Elvis Impersonator</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS GATOS, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A flashy white suit and cape made for
Elvis Presley to wear in his 1973 ``Aloha from Hawaii'' concert has
been stolen, according to the Presley impersonator who bought it for
